mMnY pwvih moKu duAwru ]
pRBU dI AwigAw dw pwlx krn vwlw mukqI dw drvwzw pw lYNdw hY[
The faithful find the Door of Liberation.
pwvih = l`B lYNdy hn[ moKu duAwru = mukqI dw drvwzw, 'kUV' qoN ^lwsI pwx dw rwh[
jy mn ivc pRBU dy nwm dI lgn l`g jwey, qW (mnu`K) 'kUV' qoN ^lwsI pwx dw rwh l`B lYNdy hn[

mMnY prvwrY swDwru ]
pRBU dI AwigAw dw pwlx krnhwr Awpxy swksYn nUM suDwr lYNdw hY[
The faithful uplift and redeem their family and relations.
prvwrY = prvwr nUM[ swDwru = AwDwr sihq krdw hY, (Akwl purK dI) tyk idRVH krwauNdw hY[
(ieho ijhw mnu`K) Awpxy prvwr nUM BI (Akwl purK dI) tyk idRVH krwauNdw hY[

mMnY qrY qwry guru isK ]
pRBU dw hukm mMnx vwlw Awpxy Awp nUM bcw lYNdw hY Aqy gurU dy is`KW dw pwr auqwrw kr idMdw hY[
The faithful are saved, and carried across with the Sikhs of the Guru.
qrY guru = gurU Awip qrdw hY[ isK = is`KW nUM[ qwry isK = is`KW nUM qwrdw hY[
nwm ivc mn pqIjx krky hI, siqgurU (BI Awp sMswr-swgr qoN) pwr lMG jWdw hY qy is`KW nUM pwr lMGwauNdw hY[

mMnY nwnk Bvih n iBK ]
pRBU dw hukm mMnx vwlw mMgdw ipMndw nhIN iPrdw[
The faithful, O Nanak, do not wander around begging.
Bvih n = nhIN BONdy[ Bvih n iBK = iB`iKAw leI nhIN BONdy iPrdy, loVW dI ^wqr dr-dr nhIN ruldy iPrdy, iDr iDr dI muQwjI nhIN krdy iPrdy[
nwm ivc mn juVn kr ky, hy nwnk! mnu`K iDr iDr dI muQwjI nhIN krdy iPrdy[

AYsw nwmu inrMjnu hoie ]
AYho ijhw hY vwihgurU dw-bydwg nwm[
Such is the Name of the Immaculate Lord.
